        Your trusted partner in industrial automation, electrical, and instrumentation solutions.
        Serving industries including Sugar, Pharma, Cement, Paper, Food & Beverage, Metals & Mining.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/machinery/"
          class="bg-brand-gold text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-md hover:bg-brand-gold-dark transition-colors font-medium text-lg"
        >
          Explore Machinery
        </a>
        <a
          href="/contact/"
