        Our Solutions
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <a href="/machinery/electrical/" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all border border-gray-200 hover:border-brand-gold">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-gold mb-2">Electrical</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray">Complete range of electrical products including VFDs, motors, transformers, and control components.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/machinery/automation/" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all border border-gray-200 hover:border-brand-gold">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-gold mb-2">Automation</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray">Advanced automation solutions including PLCs, HMIs, industrial PCs, and robotic systems.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/machinery/instrumentation/" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all border border-gray-200 hover:border-brand-gold">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-gold mb-2">Instrumentation</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray">Comprehensive instrumentation for flow, level, pressure, and temperature measurement.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <section class="bg-brand-cream py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-black mb-6">About Us</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray mb-4">
